            <div class="title">
                Small Arms (Calibre)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1951-04-25/debates/6831b7d9-efcf-4df3-ae23-38d16d9f345b/ServiceWidows(Pensions)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
